表格模具模次记录的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('tblMouldHistory')
and type = 'U')
drop table tblMouldHistory
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: tblMouldHistory */
/*==============================================================*/
create table tblMouldHistory (
DispatchNo varchar(50) not null,
MouldNo varchar(30) null,
TotalNum int not null,
BeginDate datetime null,
EndDate datetime null,
constraint PK_TBLMOULDHISTORY primary key (DispatchNo, TotalNum)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'模具模次记录表，为报表所用',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'tblMouldHistory'
go
